Security
	- OWASP Top 10 : https://www.cloudflare.com/learning/security/threats/owasp-top-10/
		-- Injection : SQL Injection Attack
		-- Broken Authentication: 2-factor Authentication, Apptemt Rate Limiting
		-- Sensitive Data Exposure :  Encryption of sensitive data, Avoid Caching Such data in cookies
		-- XML External Entities : Avoid XEE attacks using other format like JSON
		-- Broken Access Control: use Authorization Tokens
		-- Security Misconfiguarion
		-- Cross-Site Scripting
		-- Insecure Deserialization
		-- Using Components With Known Vulnerabilities
		-- Insufficient Logging And Monitoring
	- encryption
	- I/0 Sanitization

